data.description: If you are looking for country living at its best, this is the home for you! This property offers more than 6.5 acres, a gorgeous pasture, full barn with stables and hay storage, an IN-GROUND POOL, with outdoor kitchen, bath, fireplace, plus so much more! A rocking chair front porch, greets you as you enter this 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home. Wood paneled walls, beamed ceilings, a gas log fireplace, along with an open layout with an updated kitchen complete this cozy charmer. Bring your own ideas and decor to make this farmhouse a dreamhouse!
